data: Hey guys, its been {since} since the last game. You're not being paid to just sit around...
I'm not counting or anything, but the last game was over {since} ago... C'mon...
My rod's getting rusty out here.
I'd love a coffee. If only I had a big coffee machine nearby...
If nobody's going to play with me, I'm going home...
Come and check out the keepers new haircut...
It's hard to beat a person who never gives up
It isn't the mountains ahead to climb that wear you out, it's the pebble in your shoe.
You only live once, but if you play enough foosball, once is enough.
Don't hit the ball, be the ball...
